programme.title: Memori: Calon Isteri
programme.desc: Kisah Harris yang akan dinaikkan pangkat di syarikat tetapi perlu memenuhi kriteria syarikat iaitu sudah berkahwin. Cerewet dalam memilih calon isteri, akhirnya dia bertunang dengan seorang gadis kampung, Odah yang berperwatakan lasak. Namun begitu dia merancang untuk memutuskan pertunangan kerana sifat cerewetnya dan tak tahan dengan sikap lasak gadis tersebut. Setelah beberapa ketika, Odah menjadi pelakon dan semakin popular. Setelah melihat kecantikan Odah di surat khabar, dia kembali tertawan dengan perubahan gadis itu yang kini lebih bersifat feminin. Berjayakah Harris memikat hati Odah semula? Pelakon: Reen Rahim, Zahiril Adzim, Azrel Ismail, Liza Abdullah, Delimawati, dan Fathil Dani.

programme.title: Widuri : Zuriat Dari Penjara Ep16
programme.desc: Zaman dan Erina di amanahkan menjaga zuriat dari penjara. Zuriat itu adalah dari isteri pertamanya Shara yang di penjarakan kerana kesalahan mengedar dadah. Dalam episod ini Zaman telah mendapat pekerjaan baru di Johor. Shara tinggal di Kuala Lumpur seorang diri. Shara berasa berat hati melepaskan Zaman untuk bekerja di Johor kerana berasakan ini adalah pertemuan terakhir mereka. Melissa berkahwin dengan Dr. Azlan. Semasa membuat penghantara barang ke Melaka, Shara telah singgah berjumpa ibubapanya. Shara telah memohon maaf pada mereka berdua. Ibubapanya telah dapat menerima Shara. Lakonan Wafariena Roslan, Josiah Hogan, Rasya Dean, Linda Rafar, Syed Aiman, Addam Roslan, Nurul Harisyah,Mubarak Majid, Aliza Rafar, JC Lim dalam WIDURI #ZuriatDariPenjara

programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah kehidupan sekumpulan kanak-kanak semasa zaman persekolahan hingga dewasa. Razlan dihantar oleh ibu bapanya ke kampung untuk tinggal bersama atuk dan neneknya. Ibu dan bapanya ke luar negara selama dua bulan atas urusan kerja. Di kampung, Razlan mendapat kawan baru iaitu Roy, Remy, Kuzie dan Lim. Razlan seronok tinggal di kampung atuknya. Razlan melakukan banyak aktiviti bersama kawan-kawannya seperti bermain basikal, memancing, bermain bola dan sebagainya. Namun, Razlan tidak lama berada di kampung kerana perlu mengikut ibu dan bapanya ke London. Razlan berada dalam dilema. Pelakon: Nik Adam Mika, Aman Graseka, Olan Lam, Ily Mokhtar, Rosedah Amsar, Muhammad Hadi Putra, Muhammad Iskandar Zulkarnain, dan Muhammad Redzwan Adha.

programme.title: Iris Wanita
programme.desc: Membesarkan anak-anak di dlm era serba mencabar ini, kadangkala memberi tekanan kepada ibu bapa. Faktor sekeliling juga menjadikan ibu atau bapa serba tidak kena dlm mendidik anak-anak. Pelbagai usaha dilakukan, namun ada ketikanya gagal dlm membentuk keperibadian anak sehinggakan ibu bapa sendiri menjadi stress dan mengganggu kesihatan mental. Untuk itu, ibu bapa disarankan untuk mengenal pasti potensi anak-anak agar kita lebih tahu pendekatan yg sesuai dlm mendidik mereka bersama tetamu jemputan Dr Noor Aishah Rosli dalam #IrisWanita

programme.desc: Rasya Aleeya hadir dalam satu majlis prom night. Rasya Aleeya berjalan sendirian dengan memakai dress hitam dengan rambut panjang dilepaskan. Wajah Rasya juga ditutupi dengan topeng muka. Semua hadirin memakai topeng menutupi wajah. Rasya Aleeya terus berjalan. Seorang lelaki (Syed Reeza) memakai topeng muka mengajak Rasya menari. Rasya belum bersedia untuk berjumpa dengan mana-mana lelaki. Rasya takut ekoran rasa panaroid. Rasya teringat lagi semasa mama tinggalkan dirinya.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep31
programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang kali terakhir bergaduh dan membatalkan perjanjian itu, terkejut apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa mereka akan bekerjasama. Ozan, yang menyaksikan detik-detik ini, tidak tahu apa yang perlu dilakukan. Adalah sangat penting bagi Ozan untuk bekerjasama dengan Ezgi, walaupun dia bercakap dengan zgr dan cuba membetulkan keadaan ia tidak berjaya. Sementara itu, kejutan kedua menanti Ezgi. Dalam menghadapi kejadian ini, Ezgi menyoal dirinya sendiri dan menganggap dia bertindak salah dengan zgr. Dia mahu membetulkan hubungannya dengan zgr. Keinginan Ezgi untuk datang ke majlis perkahwinan membuatkan zgr gembira. Kedua-duanya bersedia untuk bermain permainan, tidak menyedari apa yang akan berlaku kepada mereka.

programme.title: Jalan-Jalan Makan Angin (2019) Ep07
programme.desc: Pengacara Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero menjelajah ke Selangor sambil mempromosi beberapa tempat penginapan dilengkapi kemudahan dan aktiviti menarik bagi percutian dan pelancongan. Antaranya ialah: 1. Sarang By The Brook, K. Kubu Bharu : -Konsep kontena dikelilingi hutan alam semulajadi, kemudahan asas termasuk penghawa dingin dan tempat tidur. -Bilik serendah RM180/ malam. -Aktiviti : Jungle tracking, mandi sungai. 2. Dusun Bonda, Batang Kali : -Konsep berkhemah dikelilingi kolam dan alam semulajadi, suasana kampung, penghawa dingin, private garden, tandas peribadi -Bilik studio : tandas persendirian, dapur, sungai, -Aktiviti : BBQ, makan malam di atas bumbung dengan suasana romantik, sarapan pagi di tepi sungai, melihat ladang madu kelulut. -Bilik serendah RM350/ malam.

programme.title: Perang Bibir Ep11
programme.desc: Nabila Huda dan Issey kembali bersaing. Nabila Huda, yang mengetuai kumpulan perempuan, digandingkan bersama Sherry Al-Hadad dan Ramona Zam Zam menentang kumpulan lelaki yang dipimpin oleh Issey yang digandingkan bersama Dennis Yin dan Izzue Islam. Kedua dua kumpulan perlu menari sepadan dengan rentak lagu yang dimainkan. Markah akan diambil kira daripada kekuatan jeritan para penonton. Pertandingan untuk memenangi RM6,000 sememangnya susah kerana peserta juga perlu bersaing di dalam 2 mini games. Markah tertinggi di penghujung rancangan akan menjadi juara untuk episod ini. Kumpulan lelaki yang mengumpul lebih markah telah diistihar sebagai pemenang.

programme.title: Trend Setter S4 Ep02
programme.desc: Episod Trend Setter kali ini Nabil akan berjumpa dengan pelumba basikal Negara, Sofian Nabil Omar. Nabil juga akan berjumpa dengan pengumpul jersey vintage Malaysia yang mempunyai jersey-jersey Malaysia yang sukar ditemui dan didapati.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep25
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam (Angah) dan Mizan (Along) dua beradik dari satu keluarga. Nizam lulusan luar negeri, bekerjaya, baru berkahwin dan baru juga bercerai. Hubungan Nizam dan Mizan tidak mesra sangat. ibu bapa mereka juga memelihara Hani, sebagai adik angkat. Kini, Hani seorang gadis, selain sangat disayangi ibu bapa mereka, Mizan pula mencintainya. Jalinan percintaan mereka juga direstui ibu bapa mereka, cuma Nizam terpaksa menangguhkan perkahwinan mereka sekurang-kurangnya 3 tahun kerana melanjutkan pelajaran keluar negara. Hani yang baik sahsiahnya dan berbudi pekerti, pandai mengemas rumah tangga memahaminya dan sanggup menunggu. Di hari ketibaan Nizam pulang, ibu bapanya telah menetapkan sebagai hari perkahwinan Nizam dan Hani. Selain majlis telah siap, tetamu juga telah dijemput, tiba-tiba sehari sebelum majlis berlangsung, Nizam meminta majlis dibatalkan dengan alasan dia telah berkahwin 5 bulan lalu. Di hari itu, Mizan juga pulang sebagai meraikan majlis adiknya, lalu ibu bapanya mencadangkan Mizan menggantikan tempat Nizam. Mizan agak terkejut dan tidak bersetuju walau pun dirayu demi menutup maruah keluarga. Sementara itu Hani amat berduka, tetapi sebelah malamnya Hani berubah hati semata-mata demi maruah keluarga lalu merayu beberapa kali kepada Mizan mengambilnya sebagai isteri. Mizan bukan sahaja menolak permintaan Hani, sebaliknya mencerca Hani yang dianggap tidak malu. Hani pula terus berdoa. Di awal pagi hari majlis, Mizan berubah hati dan bersetuju. Majlis perkahwinan Mizan dan Hani serta jamuan berjalan lancar. Di sebelah petangnya. Nizam dan isterinya, Shela juga tiba dan mereka dijangka akan tinggal di situ beberapa ketika.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep41
programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang melihat polis di hadapan mereka, terkejut. zgr, yang menganggap Tolga mengadu tentang Ezgi, menjadi gila. Mereka semua perlu pergi ke balai polis bersama-sama. Walaupun Ezgi, yang keterangannya diambil, dikeluarkan, mereka tidak melepaskan kerja ini dan cuba membuktikan Ezgi tidak bersalah. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian. Sementara itu, Ezgi telah menyediakan pesta bujang mengejut untuk Cansu. Cansu sangat gembira dapat berseronok dengan gadis-gadis itu. Emre juga tidak berdiam diri dan menyediakan kejutan untuk Levent. Tetapi kejutan ini tidak akan menggembirakan gadis-gadis itu.

programme.title: Secebis Rindu Ep02
programme.desc: Reeza pandai bermain dengan situasi hingga membuatkan Rasya selesa dengan Reeza. Rasya mula dibuai oleh perasaan atas layanan baik & mesra oleh Reeza. Reeza mahu berjumpa dengan Rasya dan jawapan Rasya pantas menjawab TIDAK. Opah beritahu Rasya yang dia nak jodohkan Rasya dengan Fahmi. programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep21
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila dan Nizam melawat Hani di hospital akibat keguguran. Di perkarangan hospital, Nizam meminta Sheila masuk dahulu. Ketika inilah Nizam diugut oleh lelaki upahan Suraya. Hubungan Nizam dan Sheila masih tegang dan dingin.. Seterusnya Nizam memaksa dan ugut Suraya agar mengaku angkara ugutan diupahnya, malahan meminta Suraya akui juga anaknya itu anak luar nikah. Suraya sekadar menidakkan dan Nizam masih bekeras. Tatkala ibu, bapa, Mizan, Hani dan turut ada Nizam berbincang di mana ibu mereka berharap Hani berpantang dan terus tinggal di rumah Sheila dan Mizan pula belum pulih, Nizam amat menyokong. Sebaliknya Hani dan Mizan tidak setuju membuatkan perasaan Nizam marah, lebih-lebih lagi hubungan Hani dan Mizan semakin mesra dan saling sayang menyayangi. Dengan sedikit ruang Nizam bertemu Hani terus menagih kasih Hani. Sambil itu menyindir Hani yang sebegitu mesra dengan Mizan.. Secara berhemah Datin Umairah menangguh projek Dato Fuad dan meminta Shariff menyiasat teliti. Sementara itu Datin Umairah sedang dan akan membantu Shariff tentang hasrat Shariff terhadap Hani. Cuma Shariff diminta bersabar kerana selain Datin Umairah berharap ujian DNA dapat dibuat, dia sendiri akan menyiasat kerana diyakini Hani adik kandung Shariff. Mizan kini amat menyayangi Hani berharap Hani ke pejabatnya untuk menyemak jawatan yang dipohonnya, seterusnya dapat bekerja dibawah penyeliaan Datin Umairah.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep22
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam keluar wad serta di terima baik ibu Sheila. Sheila meminta Nizam bersabar kerana dia perlu memantau kesihatan dan menyambung urusan kerja perniagaan bapanya. Semasa berkereta, Sheila ternampak Hani bersama Shariff dan mengambil gambar. Sheila tidak tahu menahu Shariff terpaksa mencari dan menemui Hani kerana ingin memberitahu dan menyampaikan hasil siasatan DNA bahawa mereka dua beradik. Hani masih sangsi dan mengarapkan pengesahan lagi. Shariff pula terpaksa bergegas berkaitan siasatan skandal Dato Fuad dan Suraya dan Hani ingin membantunya dituruti Kalsom (penyiasat upahan Shariff). Sheila pula memajukan gambar itu kepada Nizam agar jangan lagi mengharap Hani. Terdahulu Mizan meluahkan rasa hatinya kepada Dzul, dia ingin berhenti kerja berikutan sikap isterinya yang berbaik dengan Shariff. Semasa Shariff, Hani dan Kalsom tiba di bawah bangunan di mana Dato Fuad dan Suraya berada, bapa Shariff juga tiba dan dia terus bersama penguatkuasa Jabatan Ugama semasa Dato Fuad dan Suraya ditahan. Kemudiannya ketika Datin Umairah bersama Shariff, bapa Shariff (abang datin Umairah), Hani dan kalsom berbincang, Datin Umairah menerangkan usaha yang dibuatnya sehingga dapat tahu status Hani. Sebaliknya bapa Shariff menyarankan selidiki lagi. Hani merayu dan berharap jangan sama sekali anggapkan dia ingin mengambil kesempatan.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep23
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam bertemu Suraya dan mengugutnya, kemudiannya Nizam ditikam dan jatuh terhentak kepalanya dan tidak sedarkan diri, kini berada di wad hospital. Mizan dan Hani melawatnya dan Sheila yang merungut banyak dugaannya ditenang oleh Hani. Sebelum itu Sheila yang mengiringi ibunya ke rumah (selepas discharge) berterus terang situasinya dengan Nizam dan mengakui keluarga Nizam amat baik. Ibu Sheila kelihatan menerima hakikat merestuinya. Sementara Sheila terus menemani Nizam yang masih tidak sedarkan diri, dia juga merayu dan meratapi akan kelakuan dan kesilapan lalunya dan kesal. Hani dan Mizan singgah berbual di kedai minuman, Hani kebetulan terjumpa sahabat karibnya Kalsom dan menceritakan kepada Mizan, semasa inilah Mizan berubah dan bertanya Hani yang tidak pernah menceritakan hubungannya dengan Shariff. Hani menjelaskan segalanya dan merayu memujuk Mizan yang kelihatan merajuk pula. Sebenarnya semasa Nizam bersemuka dan berbual dengan Suraya, Nizam merakam dan dia memajukan kepada Hani. Ini membuatkan Hani dan Mizan ketahui. Mereka berdua bergegas menemui Nizam, walau pun dia mulai sedar tetapi ingatannya masih terganggu. Sementara itu apa yang dilakukan Dato Fuad telah dibayangi Datin Umairah. Datin Umairah terus tenang dan berdiam tetapi meminta Shariff terus bertindak.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep25
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam (Angah) dan Mizan (Along) dua beradik dari satu keluarga. Nizam lulusan luar negeri, bekerjaya, baru berkahwin dan baru juga bercerai. Hubungan Nizam dan Mizan tidak mesra sangat. ibu bapa mereka juga memelihara Hani, sebagai adik angkat. Kini, Hani seorang gadis, selain sangat disayangi ibu bapa mereka, Mizan pula mencintainya. Jalinan percintaan mereka juga direstui ibu bapa mereka, cuma Nizam terpaksa menangguhkan perkahwinan mereka sekurang-kurangnya 3 tahun kerana melanjutkan pelajaran keluar negara. Hani yang baik sahsiahnya dan berbudi pekerti, pandai mengemas rumah tangga memahaminya dan sanggup menunggu. Di hari ketibaan Nizam pulang, ibu bapanya telah menetapkan sebagai hari perkahwinan Nizam dan Hani. Selain majlis telah siap, tetamu juga telah dijemput, tiba-tiba sehari sebelum majlis berlangsung, Nizam meminta majlis dibatalkan dengan alasan dia telah berkahwin 5 bulan lalu. Di hari itu, Mizan juga pulang sebagai meraikan majlis adiknya, lalu ibu bapanya mencadangkan Mizan menggantikan tempat Nizam. Mizan agak terkejut dan tidak bersetuju walau pun dirayu demi menutup maruah keluarga. Sementara itu Hani amat berduka, tetapi sebelah malamnya Hani berubah hati semata-mata demi maruah keluarga lalu merayu beberapa kali kepada Mizan mengambilnya sebagai isteri. Mizan bukan sahaja menolak permintaan Hani, sebaliknya mencerca Hani yang dianggap tidak malu. Hani pula terus berdoa. Di awal pagi hari majlis, Mizan berubah hati dan bersetuju. Majlis perkahwinan Mizan dan Hani serta jamuan berjalan lancar. Di sebelah petangnya. Nizam dan isterinya, Shela juga tiba dan mereka dijangka akan tinggal di situ beberapa ketika.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep37
programme.desc: Selepas semua kekecewaan Ezgi menuju ke Bursa untuk membersihkan kepalanya. Nevin dan nal mempersoalkan keadaan Ezgi ini. Walaupun Ezgi menyembunyikan pengalamannya dengan zgr, semuanya terbongkar apabila zgr datang ke Bursa. Permohonan maaf zgr tidak mengubah apa-apa. zgr tidak mempercayainya, yang menyebabkan dia sangat kecewa. Cansu dan Deniz juga kecewa dan menyesal kerana mereka melayan Ezgi dengan salah. Mereka juga bekerjasama dengan Ozan dan cuba membawa Ezgi dan zgr bersama.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep38
programme.desc: Ezgi sangat terharu dengan kejutan zgr. Semua kebencian terhadap zgr berlalu. Dalam proses ini, kedua-duanya lebih memahami betapa mereka menghargai satu sama lain. Mereka membuka lembaran baru dalam hubungan mereka, tidak ada lagi tempat untuk pembohongan. Jadi mereka memutuskan untuk memberitahu keluarga mereka bahawa mereka bersama. Nevin menerima perhubungan ini walaupun dia tidak menginginkannya sangat, Sevim pula tidak mahu Ezgi dan zgr bersama. Ezgi mengadakan acara pertamanya di syarikat organisasi yang diupahnya, dan kejutan menantinya di acara ini. Sementara itu, Serdar mengambil tindakan sekali lagi untuk mendapatkan Ezgi, tetapi apabila dia mengetahui bahawa zgr dan Ezgi bersama, dia kecewa dan keadaan ini menjadikannya lebih bercita-cita tinggi.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep39
programme.desc: zgr menjadi marah apabila dia mengetahui bahawa Tolga ialah bos Ezgi. Ezgi segera berhenti. Tetapi Tolga tidak akan selesa sehingga dia mendapat La Gabbia, dia telah pun membuat perancangan untuk meletakkan Ezgi dalam situasi yang sukar dengan sokongan Gizem. Dia mengambil kesempatan daripada kelemahan zgr untuk Ezgi. Apabila bercakap mengenai Ezgi, ia menjadi lebih sukar bagi zgr untuk membuat keputusan menentang kehendak Tolga. Sementara itu, zgr berurusan dengan restoran baharu dan pembukaannya. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep40
programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang melihat polis di hadapan mereka, terkejut. zgr, yang menganggap Tolga mengadu tentang Ezgi, menjadi gila. Mereka semua perlu pergi ke balai polis bersama-sama. Walaupun Ezgi, yang keterangannya diambil, dikeluarkan, mereka tidak melepaskan kerja ini dan cuba membuktikan Ezgi tidak bersalah. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian. Sementara itu, Ezgi telah menyediakan pesta bujang mengejut untuk Cansu. Cansu sangat gembira dapat berseronok dengan gadis-gadis itu. Emre juga tidak berdiam diri dan menyediakan kejutan untuk Levent. Tetapi kejutan ini tidak akan menggembirakan gadis-gadis itu.

programme.desc: Selepas bertemu Serdar di Gcek, Ezgi dan zgr mula berfikir tentang apa yang perlu dilakukan apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa Serdar juga akan menghadiri majlis perkahwinan Ebru. Rakan-rakan mereka cuba mencari idea dan membantu mereka untuk meneruskan perkahwinan. programme.title: Rock 4: Rockers Never Dai
programme.desc: Filem ini mengisahkan liku-liku kehidupan yang dilalui oleh bekas ahli kumpulan muzik rock terkenal di era 90an, Rimba Bara. Namun kerana gejala dadah, masalah peribadi yang tidak terkawal dan kemalangan ngeri yang menimpa, kehidupan anggota kumpulan musnah. Seorang yang koma kembali sedar, membawa sinar baru apabila dia berjaya menguruskan kumpulan muzik rock baru menggunakan nama kumpulan lama; Rimba Bara II diterajui oleh pemuda yang juga jirannya. Pelbagai cabaran dan halangan ditempuhi sebelum kumpulan mereka berjaya dan menempa nama dalam industri muzik rock tanah air. programme.desc: Traces the current affairs from china and the world

programme.title: Bond with China Ep50
programme.desc: Bond with China, which is produced by China Media Group China Central Television International Channel, is a large-scale intercultural communication documentary program.

programme.title: Network News

programme.title: In the Family (T) Ep265266
programme.desc: "Home" as axis X and "love" as axis Y, this piece exquisitely depicts the ups and downs in life of an ordinary family. From touching sibling love, to the struggles and entanglement of parent-child relationship, the show elaborates on the importance of encountering the surroundings with a positive attitude. Through a bowl of beef noodle soup, Hui-wen and Chien-chin teach their four daughters, Spring, Summer, Fall, and Winter, how to behave around others. The heartwarming play is relaxing, fun, humorous, and a tearjerker.

programme.desc: Brand new concept of a travelogue show! Hosts will be using a different perspectives and knowledge to show you the latest tourist spots to check in!

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep888889
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: The Borderless World (M) Ep700
programme.desc: Journalist with an infallible nose for a story is leading the audience to explore the world. Exploring how people from different cultures overcome the challenges with collective wisdom.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep476
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Happy Enemy(M) Ep3233
programme.desc: Pei-Pei Wu and Yu-Hsuan Lee have been comparing with each other since childhood. They had a crush on each other but later became rivals because of an accident. They both wished each other would disappear from their lives; however, they are neighbors. Pei-Pei and Yu-Hsuan have been fighting, yet they inevitably fell into the destined love with each other. If fighting against each other is a way of communication and caring, then these quarrelsome lovers are getting closer and growing together. When they gradually start to let go of their competitive attitude that is full of hostility, they even start to click with each other!

programme.title: Integrity
programme.desc: Anti-corruption senior officer Chen lines up a key witness, corporate accountant Jack, to testify against a tobacco trading company CEO for bribing high-level customs officer as well as smuggling contraband cigarettes. When neither Jack nor the CEO shows up on the day of the hearing, Chen must team up with his ex-wife to launch an investigation.

programme.title: Big Brother
programme.desc: Henry Chen, a former soldier, is recruited for his toughest mission yet - teaching a class of teen delinquents. As he kicks his way into their school and home lives, it becomes clear that his unconventional teaching style might be just what they need.

programme.title: Paws-Men
programme.desc: When a dog is in need of rescue, the Paws-Men assemble to save the dog like Batman. Paws-Men tells the story of four men rescuing dogs and the many difficulties that they encounter, from a dog eatery to bullies and a dog abusing granny. Despite the hardships, Paws-Men give us a peek into the true friendships between dogs and humans.

programme.title: Bangkok Storm
programme.desc: Underground boxer Lin Feng is hunted by the Bangkok triad when he refuses to fight in an illegal match. He escaped successfully but lost his memory. While Feng begins a new life, the triad finds him and hires a top boxer to beat him. As Feng suddenly regains his memory in the process, he vows to take down the triad.

programme.title: All's Well End's Well 2012
programme.desc: This beloved slapstick comedy series continues as it follows four couples who meet through a dating website. Four men go on a heroic mission to help four women and wind up experiencing a series of mishaps.

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighboring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: Wu Xia
programme.desc: Martial artist Liu hides his identity and lives in a remote village with his wife Ah Yu and their two sons, but somehow gets embroiled in a bizarre murder case. Constable Xu is a kung fu fanatic, whose curiosity forces Liu into a death duel with the Sect Leader of the 72 Demons, and puts Lius family and homeland in a great danger...

programme.title: Secret Diary of a Mom To Be, The
programme.desc: A high-flying PR manager and her loving husband swear by a childless lifestyle but she is shocked to learn that she is expecting just when things look bright for a promotion! How would they deal with the unexpected surprises that life throws in their way?

programme.title: Kill Mobile
programme.desc: Seven friends get together and decide to play a game where they must share all the messages, calls and app notifications on each other's cell phones. Hilarity and drama follows as everyone's secrets are unveiled throughout the evening, and the seven friends find themselves more like strangers to each other than ever before!

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kongs Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: Miao Miao
programme.desc: Miao Miao is an awkward young beauty who nevertheless enchants her outgoing classmate Xiao Ai. As Xiao Ais feelings for Miao Miao grows from friendship to something more, Miao Miao discovers her own burgeoning attraction to a sullen CD store owner, and quietly pursues him.

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: Seobok
programme.desc: Former secret agent Ki Hun is entrusted with a secret mission to escort the first human clone, Seobok, to a safe place. Seobok, who possesses a life-preserving DNA that could save humanity, explores the outside world with Ki Hun for the first time but they are both chased and claimed as terrorists by CIA. How can Ki Hun protect Seobok from danger?

programme.title: The Sunny Side of the Street
programme.desc: Hassan is a Pakistani refugee boy whose father has died in a car accident. A local taxi driver, Yat, then helps him flee Hong Kong. In the process, the two gradually develop a father-son relationship, until Hassan discovers the shocking truth about his fathers death

programme.title: The Lost Bladesman
programme.desc: An epic historic adventure set during the turbulent times of the Three Kingdoms. Cao Cao attempts to enlist Guan Yu into his forces, but Guan is loyal to his sworn brother Liu Bei, who is also Caos enemy. As Guan tries to rescue Liu Beis concubine from Cao, he is forced to fight his way through. Can he succeed in the end?

programme.title: You are the One
programme.desc: A talented rogue trader experiences a 180-degree change in life when he encounters a girl who does not believe good things will happen to her. Will they fall in love? It seems like a Cinderellas adventure has just begun!

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kits master, Debo.

programme.title: Project Gutenberg
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police hunts for a counterfeiting gang led by a mastermind known as Painter. The gang is so skillful that it's almost impossible to distinguish between its counterfeit currency and real money. In an effort to find Painter's real identity, the Police recruits artist Lee Man to assist in solving the case.

programme.title: The Knight of Shadows: Between Yin and Yang
programme.desc: Pu Song Ling, a legendary demon hunter, is asked to investigate a case involving missing teenage village girls with disciple, Constable Yan Fei. The duo leads a group of little monsters to help with the investigation, and in their search for the truth, they accidentally discover a mysterious love between a knight and a female ghost.

programme.title: Bodies at Rest
programme.desc: When three armed criminals barge into a morgue, a forensic doctor and his student must fight with their lives to stop the criminals from obtaining a bullet from inside a corpse that is a key piece of evidence in a deadly crime.

programme.title: Echoes of the Rainbow
programme.desc: Set in Hong Kong in the 1960s, the story revolves around the family of a hardworking shoemaker Mr Law, with his happy-go-lucky wife and two sons a talented elder son and an eight-year-old eccentric younger son. While their lives are not always smooth-sailing, the family sticks together and support one another through thick and thin.

programme.title: Night and Fog
programme.desc: Following The Way We Are, this is based on a true story happening in Tin Shui Wai. It revolves around an older, unemployed Hong Kong man, his young Mainland wife and their two daughters. Their lives, unfortunately, are anything but easy, and the shocking conclusion raises issues about the plight of the socially deprived lower class.

programme.title: Love and Let Love!
programme.desc: Cliff proposes to his girlfriend Terry but is killed in a car accident before she says yes. Terry is devastated and inconsolable. When Cliff's ghost returns, they seem to go back to their good old days. However, Cliff is determined to help Terry get over his death and start anew.

programme.title: Viral
programme.desc: Following the outbreak of a virus that wipes out the majority of the human population, a young woman documents her family's new life in quarantine and tries to protect her infected sister.

programme.title: The Captain
programme.desc: The movie is based on a real incident of Sichuan Airlines Flight 8633 on 14 May 2018. When the cockpit windshield shatters after takeoff, the Captain manages to land the airplane safely with his level-headed swift actions and sheer determination. This is lauded as a miracle in airline history.

programme.title: The Mad Monk
programme.desc: Stephen Chow plays an arrogant god in Heaven who is being punished for his pranks and mistakes. He is sent to Earth and reincarnate as Mad Monk to change the destiny of three misguided souls - a prostitute, a beggar and a villain. The Mad Monk needs to complete the task in three days in order to return to Heaven.

programme.title: Young and Dangerous: Reloaded
programme.desc: In this remake of Young and Dangerous, Chan Ho Nam and his three buddies of the Hung Hing triad gang strive to fight for their own justice, further expanding their power in the triad and becoming a new legend...

programme.title: The Comeback
programme.desc: Uncle Hua is a retired agent who owns an antique shop on an old street. When the old street is forcibly demolished by the local Green Dragon Gang one day, Uncle Huas hidden identity is accidentally revealed, and he is pursued by a mysterious organization headed by Ah Jie. A fatal duel has just begun!

programme.title: The Narrow Road
programme.desc: Chak, a small cleaning company owner, hits tough times during the pandemic. In need of an assistant, he hires a young single mother Candy, who unexpectedly helps him solve many difficulties at work. While life seems to get back on track, a series of cruel realities happen again, but they still bond together to support each other on the narrow road.

programme.title: Detective Vs. Sleuths
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of cold-blooded murders whose victims are runaway suspects of unsolved cases. The group of killers calls themselves The Chosen Sleuths". Former top detective Lee vows to bring the brutal killers to justice and prove himself to be the real Chosen Sleuth instead of a lunatic.

programme.title: Wusong VS Ximenqing
programme.desc: Wu Song finds out about his sister-in-laws affair with a rich man, Ximen Qing. Qing sets Song up and have him exiled for a year, during which his hapless brother is murdered and cremated. When Song finally returns home, he takes the case to court but the judge brushes it aside and closes it abruptly. Can Song finally avenge his brothers death?

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: The Brave Archer 3
programme.desc: Guo Jing and Huang Rong go to Iron Palm Peak to search for the Book of Wumu. The chief of Iron Palm discovers their visit, and seriously injures Huang. It seems only the Southern Emperor Duan can heal her, but will Huang be healed in time?

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: The Blood Brothers
programme.desc: The friendship of three sworn brothers, Zhang, Huang and Ma ends when Ma gives in to corruption and falls for Huang's wife, eventually leading to a bloody ending.

programme.title: The Empress Dowager
programme.desc: Award-winning drama featuring a passionate performance by Lisa Lu, enhanced by sumptuous costumes and sets, produces a powerful, fascinating story. In five thousand years of Chinese history, there was never a more fascinating woman than the dragon lady of the Ching Dynasty, also the Empress Dowager, who was the power behind the throne for the last half of the 19th century. The vast tapestry of palace intrigues is vividly brought to the screen.

programme.title: The Killer
programme.desc: Hsieh Choun, the Black Dragon, is in trouble with the police since Wang Sien Tien's gang is helping them; he is no longer free to conduct his drugs shipments out of the port freely as he used to. He buys more thugs and killers to dispose of the young upstart, and soon Wang is in dire straits, in the port of Hong Kong.

programme.title: The Mirror And The Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: Flying Guillotine 2
programme.desc: In a time of anti-Manchu sentiment, Emperor Yong Zheng employs his ruthless Blood Hound Corps to silence any dissenters. Only one man and his signature weapon, The Flying Guillotine, stand in their way.

programme.title: Les Belles
programme.desc: Acknowledged as one of the greatest Hong Kong musicals, this lavish movie starring Linda Lin, who won Best Actress for her performance, infuses its wispy plot with style and wit, and the results are pure pleasure.

programme.title: The Long Chase
programme.desc: Governor Yan is killed and his guard Fan identifies Kou as the assassin by his signature weapon, a dart. Kou is listed as a wanted man when he enters the city, but managed to escape arrest with the help of the innkeepers daughter. At the same time, Fan is attacked by a bandit who pretends to be Kou. What are the secret plots behind these attacks?

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: Return Of Reincarnated Swordsman
programme.desc: A band of ninjas slaughters the entire Wu Dang Clan and frames Du Gu Wu Di, chief of the Invincible Clan, for the deed. Yun masters the silkworm martial arts style and decides to take revenge for the Clan by challenging Wu Di, but is defeated and seriously hurt. Luckily, Master Li saves and treats him, allowing Yun to avoid the ninjas pursuit.

programme.title: Crazy Shaolin Disciples
programme.desc: Three young kung-fu warriors from wildly different backgrounds become students of Shaolin at the same temple. These three warriors are: Royal Guard Lo Lieh, fleeing soldier, Lo Meng, and villager, Wang Yu.

programme.title: To Kill A Jaguar
programme.desc: Set in 1920s Shanghai, a village girl journeys to the big city in search of her father and meets her childhood friend Jaguar, who works for the mob boss Kam. In a world controlled by the mobs, it is a test of survival for all as Jaguar allies himself with ace gunman Ko Tang, to take over Kams empire.

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: The Enchantress
programme.desc: Shot on the Shaws' lot in the final years of Hong Kong's greatest studio, The Enchantress tells the story of martial artists who disappear in the night! Intrigued, wanna-be detective/swordsman Feng Chi-wu (Mok Siu-chung) is determined to find out what is happening. But when Feng finds out that an evil vampire spirit (Wei Chiu-hua) is killing swordsmen, he's in for more than he bargains for... It's an outlandish fairy-tale and martial arts fantasy, where your fists and sword aren't nearly enough!

programme.title: The Last Tempest
programme.desc: This sequel to The Empress Dowager continues the tale of Emperor Guangxu and Empress Dowager Cixi. Despite Guangxus enthronement, his ability to rule effectively is overshadowed by the ever-present power of Cixi. When his attempts to reform the Imperial system are thwarted by the Empress Dowager, Guangxu attempts to curb her power.

programme.title: The Chinese Boxer
programme.desc: A Japanese karate master and Diao Er, who has been expelled from his martial arts school, return to the school to kill the school master and his disciples. After the massacre, disciple Lei Ming embarks on a vigorous training regime and vows to avenge their death. A fatal battle is about to begin

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: The Mighty One
programme.desc: Lung seeks five volumes of a renowned Kung Fu manual to gain invincibility. When he believes a martial arts school master possesses the volumes, he kills him and his daughter but leaves behind a young brother and sister. Years later, Lung loses two volumes and starts another bloody hunt but each attempt is interrupted by two mysterious warriors...

programme.title: The Shepherd Girl
programme.desc: In this musical drama, Hsiu Hsiu, a beautiful shepherd girl, falls in love with a handsome boatman Ta Lung. However, she cannot afford to marry him because of her fathers towering debt from gambling. To complicate the matter, a rival suitor promises to pay off all her father's debts on one condition: that Hsiu Hsiu marries him...

programme.title: Heaven Sword And Dragon Sabre 2
programme.desc: Only by bringing together the powerful Heaven Sword and the mighty Dragon Sabre can six martial arts sects struggling for supremacy be saved in this thrilling sequel to Chu Yuan's original hit.

programme.title: The Younger Generation
programme.desc: A tragic tale about a young girl who gets married and has five kids. When she and her husband die, leaving all five kids behind to fend for themselves, the eldest child is forced to be sold into prostitution to feed the other four.

programme.title: That Fiery Girl
programme.desc: The bandits of Hulu Valley slay the chief of the Mei Clan while searching for a treasure map. In retaliation, Chun from the Mei Clan infiltrates the bandit's fortress to map a way in for the authorities, but ends up falling in love with the bandit leader's daughter, Pearl. While Chuns plot is uncovered, he receives unexpected help from Pearl.

programme.title: Diau Charn
programme.desc: In the Han Dynasty, the tyrannical Prime Minister Dong Zuo takes control of the country, so Minister Wang plots to take him down using Diau Charns beauty. Wang arranges for her to be Dongs concubine as he knows Dongs adopted son Lu Bu is in love with her, turning them against each other. Lu Bu ends up killing Dong Zuo to be with Diau Charn.

programme.title: Facets Of Love
programme.desc: Set in the Ming Dynasty, the story revolves around a brothel and the girls who work there. The film begins by following the life of a girl from a poor family, who is sold by her mother to the brothel. While she is the most beautiful of the girls and attracts many clients, the girl hopes to escape this sad way of life one day.

programme.title: The Land Of Many Perfumes
programme.desc: Monk Tang San Zang, Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing find themselves in Womanland, where women give birth to baby girls by drinking the magical spring water.

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: Heroes Two
programme.desc: Shaolin disciple Hung escapes from the burning temple after it is attacked by the Qing army and is badly wounded. He is handed over to the Qing soldiers by Fang as he mistakes Hung for a bandit. When Fang realizes his mistakes, he tries all ways to help Hung escape so that they can team up to fight the Qing army together.

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: The Spiritual Boxer
programme.desc: One of the first kung fu comedies, this is a story about a con artist who uses kung fu to swindle villagers for money by pretending to be possessed by spirits. When they are threatened by bandits, he must use the same skills for good.

programme.title: The Pearl Phoenix
programme.desc: In Huangmei Opera tradition, this movie tells the love story of Wen, who sells himself as a slave to a rich family, and Huo, the familys young daughter. The lovers are kept apart by Huos stepmother and Huo escapes by dressing up as a man. Wen is framed and put into jail so Huo has to go back and rescue her lover!

programme.title: The Lizard
programme.desc: A seasoned burglar 'The Lizard' sets himself up against a corrupt police chief and announced that he will steal a diamond from a rich mans party. His real identity, which is discovered by the corrupt police chiefs granddaughter, is actually a young policeman who is doing it all for justice.

programme.title: Gossip Street
programme.desc: All neighbours gather to gossip in flat number 8 on the second floor of the Gossip Street apartment building! Most of the residents are common people from all walks of life and there is never a lack of laughter or sarcasm in the neighbourhood. However, when a local mobster wants to change the place into a gambling den, things get serious...

programme.title: The New One-Armed Swordsman
programme.desc: David Chiang plays the all-new one-armed hero - a man who chops off his right arm rather than live with dishonor. When the love of his life is kidnapped and his best friend is murdered by the evil gang, it is time to battle.

programme.title: The Big Sting
programme.desc: Three buddies find a rare artifact known as the Double-Faced God but are poisoned by Lady Wu who steals the treasure from them. Before they die, they get their wives to promise to train their children to take back what is rightfully theirs. These kids grow up to exact a vengeance that turns out to be more hilarious than horrific in this comedy.

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep35
programme.desc: How Can I Make My Peach Soft? - JESS and the pups give Baa a peach to eat, thinking it will make a change from grass. But the peach is too hard. How can I make my peach soft? Asks Jess. That's the Big Question! He asks Mimi and watches her kneading clay. She explains she's making the clay soft. Jess tries throwing the peach in the air to soften it but all it does is bruise. Horace tells them that the water in his pond keeps his skin soft so Jess and the pups try to soften the peach in water. But it's still hard. They visit Willow who offers the pups some of her lovely ripe cherries. She explains that the cherries went soft and changed colour when they ripened. Jess realises it's the same for the peach. He waits for it to ripen and then gives it to Baa. It's delicious! And now Jess knows how to make a peach soft. Yippety yay!

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep36
programme.desc: How Can We Help Billy Stay Warm? - Jess, Mimi, Baa and Billie are playing a game, kicking a fir cone into a bucket. But it's so cold that poor shivering Billie can't kick properly. They need to find a way Bilie can stay warm enough. Baa's never cold because of his wool. They find a clump of Baa's wool on the ground but it just falls off Billie when Jess puts it on her and Mimi tells them that glueing it on's a bad idea. What happens when it's summer and Billie wants to be cool? Maybe wrapping her in it, like a blanket, is the answer? It definitely keeps her warm - only problem is, she can't move! They realise that Baa wears a scarf as well. Perhaps they need a scarf for Billie? Mimi knits a tiny scarf for Billie, after twisting the clump of wool into yarn. It's perfect! Billie's toasty warm for their game of Flying Fircones. Yippety Yay!

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep37
programme.desc: How Can We Hide To Watch Butterflies? - JESS, JOEY and JINX go to the Whispering Woods in the hope of seeing some butterflies, but the puppies are so lively and noisy that they frighten them away. JESS wonders how can we hide to watch butterflies? That's the Big Question! JESS decides to make somewhere to hide out of natural materials. The puppies and Jess try to build a hide out of stones but they're too heavy and all fall down. Jess thinks that something lighter might work well but when they try to build a hide out of straw it's TOO light and flies away in the wind. JESS is stuck - there must be some other material on Greendale Farm they could use. But all that's around them are trees. Jess works out that trees are made out of wood and there are lots of old wooden apple crates in Willow's Stable which will do the job perfectly. JESS, JOEY and JINX build a butterfly hide out of wooden apple crates and soon see lots and lots of beautiful butterflies. Yippety yay!

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep38
programme.desc: How Can I Go Faster Than Joey And Jinx? - It's a snowy day on Greendale Farm so Jess and his friends have a race down Cherry Hill. Jess wants to win the race but he can't run as fast in the snow. How can I go faster than Joey and Jinx? Thinks Jess. That's the Big Question. First, Jess tries rolling down the hill like the puppies but he's not a good roller so that doesn't work. Horace shows Jess how he slides down his slide in the pond. Jess tries again at Cherry Hill but can't get going. Helped by Billie and Baa he remembers everything that Horace did - pushing off, going Wheeeee! and lifting his legs up - but nothing works; he ends up sitting in the snow and not sliding at all. He needs something that will move on its own like Mimi's trolley! Jess tries sliding down the hill on the trolley but the wheels get stuck in the snow. Jess decides to take the wheels off and see if the trolley moves faster. Jess whizzes down the hill on the trolley top much faster than the rolling puppies. It's brilliant fun and he's answered the question. Yippety Ya
